{"id":1475252325,"question_id":3,"lang":"cpp","lang_name":"C++","time":"1 week, 2 days","timestamp":1733836164,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"0 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/1475252325/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Longest Substring Without Repeating Characters","memory":"10.3 MB","code":"class Solution {\npublic:\n    int lengthOfLongestSubstring(string s) {\n        int left=0, right=0;\n        int maxlen = 0;\n        vector<char> countarr(128, 0);\n        while(right < s.length()) {\n            while(countarr[s[right]] != 0) {\n                countarr[s[left]] = 0;\n                left++;\n            }\n            countarr[s[right]] = 1;\n            maxlen = max(maxlen, right - left + 1);\n            right++;\n        }\n        return maxlen;\n    }\n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"longest-substring-without-repeating-characters","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
